<item>
            <title>[LU-1210] Lustre error when we re-export the file system with samba</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1210</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We recive some Lustre Error on the Lustre client that re-export.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Mar 12 10:27:23 osiride-lv-040 kernel: LustreError:&lt;br/&gt;
16698:0:(file.c:3227:ll_file_flock()) unknown fcntl lock type: 32&lt;br/&gt;
Mar 12 10:27:23 osiride-lv-040 kernel: LustreError:&lt;br/&gt;
16698:0:(file.c:3227:ll_file_flock()) Skipped 421 previous similar messages&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>Lustre 1.8.7 wc1 &lt;br/&gt;
Red Hat 5.7 on the lustre servers&lt;br/&gt;
Red Hat 5.4 on the lustre clients&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
One lustre client re-export via SAMBA the file system to Windows clients&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
Samba version:&lt;br/&gt;
samba-3.0.33-3.15.el5_4.1&lt;br/&gt;
samba-common-3.0.33-3.15.el5_4.1&lt;br/&gt;
samba-client-3.0.33-3.15.el5_4.1&lt;br/&gt;
</environment>
