                            <comment id="31070" author="adilger" created="Tue, 13 Mar 2012 19:32:36 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I think Peter meant to type &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1073&quot; title=&quot;mandatory (LOCK_MAND) flock requests cause unknown fcntl lock type: 32 Lustre error messages&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-1073&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-1073&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="31050" author="pjones" created="Tue, 13 Mar 2012 13:19:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi there&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This appears to be a duplicate of &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1703&quot; title=&quot;b2_1 can&amp;#39;t pass acc-sm test&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-1703&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-1703&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. A fix has been landed to master to hide these messages so I think that it is ok to just ignore them - see &lt;a href=&quot;http://git.whamcloud.com/?p=fs/lustre-release.git;a=commitdiff;h=68570176f72515dc10875dcacd7dbdc76dff3eaa;hp=b9ccecd1453c5c76fe135048c39f149c241650c6&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://git.whamcloud.com/?p=fs/lustre-release.git;a=commitdiff;h=68570176f72515dc10875dcacd7dbdc76dff3eaa;hp=b9ccecd1453c5c76fe135048c39f149c241650c6&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Peter&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="31044" author="lustre.support" created="Tue, 13 Mar 2012 10:29:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi,&lt;br/&gt;
we some times receive some Lustre Error on the client that re-export the file system with Samba.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I have attached the smb.conf configuration. Could you help us to understand if the errors are critical and the samba/lustre right configuration to eliminate these errors ?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thanks in advance.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
